# Updating This Documentation

Procedures for keeping this documentation in sync with the **{{ org.name }}** organization configuration.

---

<details>
<summary><strong>Export Script</strong></summary>

```bash
#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

OID="{{ org.oid }}"
EXPORT_DIR="./exports/$(date +%Y-%m-%d)"
mkdir -p "$EXPORT_DIR"

echo "=== Exporting {{ org.name }} org configuration ==="

echo "Exporting sensors..."
limacharlie sensor list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/sensors.yaml"

echo "Exporting D&R rules..."
limacharlie dr list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/dr-rules.yaml"

echo "Exporting FP rules..."
limacharlie dr fp list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/fp-rules.yaml" 2>/dev/null || echo "{}" > "$EXPORT_DIR/fp-rules.yaml"

echo "Exporting AI agents..."
limacharlie hive list --hive-name ai_agent --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/ai-agents.yaml"

echo "Exporting extensions..."
limacharlie extension list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/extensions.yaml"

echo "Exporting cloud adapters..."
limacharlie cloud-adapter list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/cloud-adapters.yaml"

echo "Exporting outputs..."
limacharlie output list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/outputs.yaml"

echo "Exporting installation keys..."
limacharlie installation-key list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/installation-keys.yaml"

echo "Exporting secret names..."
limacharlie secret list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/secrets.yaml"

echo "Exporting SOPs..."
limacharlie sop list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/sops.yaml"

echo "Exporting lookups..."
limacharlie lookup list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/lookups.yaml"

echo "Exporting tags..."
limacharlie tag list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/tags.yaml"

echo "Exporting payloads..."
limacharlie payload list --oid "$OID" --output yaml > "$EXPORT_DIR/payloads.yaml"

echo ""
echo "=== Export complete: $EXPORT_DIR ==="
ls -la "$EXPORT_DIR"
```

</details>

---

<details>
<summary><strong>GitHub Actions Workflow</strong></summary>

```yaml
# .github/workflows/update-docs.yaml
name: Update LC Org Documentation
on:
  schedule:
    - cron: '0 8 * * 1'  # Every Monday at 8 AM UTC
  workflow_dispatch:

jobs:
  export-config:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - name: Install LimaCharlie CLI
        run: pip install limacharlie

      - name: Export org configuration
        env:
          LC_API_KEY: {% raw %}${{ secrets.LC_API_KEY }}{% endraw %}
          LC_OID: {{ org.oid }}
        run: bash scripts/export-org-config.sh

      - name: Check for changes
        id: changes
        run: |
          git diff --quiet exports/ || echo "changed=true" >> "$GITHUB_OUTPUT"

      - name: Commit and push
        if: steps.changes.outputs.changed == 'true'
        run: |
          git config user.name "github-actions[bot]"
          git config user.email "github-actions[bot]@users.noreply.github.com"
          git add exports/
          git commit -m "chore: weekly org config export $(date +%Y-%m-%d)"
          git push
```

</details>

