## Manual Update Procedures

### When to Update Each File

| File | Update When | Verify With |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| `sensors.md` | Sensor added/removed/status changed | `limacharlie sensor list --oid $OID --output yaml` |
| `detection-rules.md` | Rule added/removed/enabled/disabled | `limacharlie dr list --oid $OID --output yaml` |
| `ai-agents.md` | Agent added/modified/removed | `limacharlie hive list --hive-name ai_agent --oid $OID --output yaml` |
| `data-pipeline.md` | Extension subscribed/unsubscribed, output changed | `limacharlie extension list --oid $OID --output yaml` |
| `access-control.md` | Key rotated, secret added, SOP changed | `limacharlie secret list --oid $OID --output yaml` |
| `architecture.md` | Significant topology change | Review all exports |

